commit.message: Add gflags -> absl.flags migration guidelines.
Release 3.1.2.
Publish deprecation notice and point to Abseil.

Merge pull request #40 from yilei/absl

Add new API names.

Add new API names:
DEFINE_multi_string
DEFINE_multi_integer

The old APIs were renamed in github.com/abseil/abseil-py.

This is to make the transition from python-gflags to absl-py easier.
python-gflags: Release 3.1.1.
Provide PEP8 style method/function aliases.

Update Classsifiers 

The purpose is to change the status shown on Python 3 Wall Of Superpowers (https://python3wos.appspot.com/).
